<div class="xl-row xl-middle">
	<div class="fill-1 vjustify justify content">
		<div class="col vjustify gap-4">
			<div class="col justify vjustify gap-3">
				<h3>200 students. 36 hours. Limitless possibilities.</h3>
				<p>We're excited to announce CarlHacks, Carleton College's second national hackathon. Whether you've been programming for five minutes or five years, you'll find CarlHacks to be an incredible space to learn more. Bring your next big idea to life over the course of 36 hours (napping strongly encouraged), attend a cornucopia of workshops, and join an awesome community of hackers. Undergrads from any university in the US are invited.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col justify vjustify gap-3">
				<h3>Why CarlHacks?</h3>
				<ul class="col gap-1">
					<li><p>Compete in teams to <strong>win exciting prizes</strong> (last year, the members of the winning team each took home a drone)</p></li>
					<li><p>Get <strong>one-on-one help</strong> from professors and professional engineers</p></li>
					<li><p>Attend <strong>Git and web development classes</strong> for beginners, and <strong>workshops on advanced topics</strong> throughout the event</p></li>
					<li><p>Chat with companies and <strong>kickstart your internship or job search</strong></p></li>
					<li><p>Hack with Oculus Rifts, Pebble watches, Leap Motions, and more from the <strong>hardware lab</strong></p></li>
					<li><p>Eat <strong>delicious catered meals</strong>, snacks, and of course, coffee</p></li>
					<li><p>Need a coding break? Take a nap on an air mattress, a shower in our bathrooms, walk around our 880-acre arboretum, or participate in one of our exciting mini-events, complete with mini-prizes</p></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
